   <name>Tornado Watch issued October 18 at 4:42PM CDT until October 18 at 9:00PM CDT by NWS Shreveport LA</name>
   <styleUrl>#sev_extreme</styleUrl>
   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>THE NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE HAS EXTENDED TORNADO WATCH 624 TO
INCLUDE THE FOLLOWING AREAS UNTIL 9 PM CDT THIS EVENING

IN ARKANSAS THIS WATCH INCLUDES 1 COUNTY

IN SOUTH CENTRAL ARKANSAS

UNION

IN LOUISIANA THIS WATCH INCLUDES 8 PARISHES

IN NORTH CENTRAL LOUISIANA

CALDWELL              GRANT                 JACKSON
LA SALLE              LINCOLN               OUACHITA
UNION                 WINN

THIS INCLUDES THE CITIES OF BERNICE, CLARKS, COLFAX, COLUMBIA,
DRY PRONG, EL DORADO, FARMERVILLE, GRAYSON, JENA, JONESBORO,
MIDWAY, MONROE, MONTGOMERY, OLLA, RUSTON, AND WINNFIELD.</Snippet>
