   <Snippet>* WHAT...South winds around 20 kt with gusts up to 25 kt and seas
around 4 ft expected.

* WHERE...Waters from Pensacola FL to Pascagoula MS from 20 to
60 NM and Waters from Okaloosa Walton County Line FL to
Pensacola FL from 20 to 60 NM.

* WHEN...From 7 PM this evening to 7 AM CDT Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.</Snippet>
